      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels that won\u2019t break the bank? This car isn\u2019t showroom-perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who needs basic transport, a runabout, or a project with potential. It\u2019s got the honest wear you\u2019d expect from an older used car, but it still has plenty of life left for the right buyer. If you want something cheap, straightforward, and full of character, this could be a great fit. Priced to sell and ready for its next chapter.",
