      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver with strong project potential. Engine fires up willingly, transmission engages as it should, and the chassis has the kind of straightforward mechanical layout that makes upkeep approachable for a hands-on owner. Not a showroom piece, but it has usable road manners, a functional powertrain, and the kind of honest character that makes an affordable daily, learner car, or weekend tinkering platform. Priced to reflect condition while still offering plenty of value for someone who appreciates a mechanically serviceable car with room to improve.",
